@NODE HIST "History"
@PREV ACK
@{fg shine}History@{fg text}

    0.0     The very first release, with no docs, no prefs
            file, not even a copyright sign :-)

(   SBB     Steve Pearson's "SpotButtonBank" - a reworking
            of the initial release plus prefs file)

    1.0     The first release have a prefs GUI.  Slight problem
            - most users didn't have a big enough screen to view it!
            Also introduced the scrolling status bar :)

    2.0     Completely reworked preferences section.  Compacted
            configuration file.  Add listview as well as buttons.
            Added "Extra Bank", and support for Rexx/CLI/Spot commands.

    2.0a    Bug Fix.  In Prefs/Buttons, it would respond with errors
            when Add/Insert is selected.
@ENDNODE
